                    <h3 class="mtext-111 cl2 p-b-16">
                        Our Mission
                    </h3>

                    <p class="stext-113 cl6 p-b-26">
                        We believe true style starts with respect—respect for people and the planet. Our mission is to nurture Chişinău’s creative community by providing fair wages, zero-waste workshops, and mentorship programs for emerging artisans. Every collection we launch reflects seasonal cycles, from flax-green spring linen dresses to hand-woven wool coats for winter’s chill. By championing transparency at every step—from farm to finishing stitch—we aim to inspire others to choose quality over quick fashion.
                    </p>

                    <p class="stext-113 cl6 p-b-26">
                        Beyond clothing, we’re committed to giving back: a portion of each sale supports local educational initiatives in rural Moldova, helping young students learn design and textile skills. Together with our partners, we host annual “Design for Change” hackathons, where teams reimagine traditional motifs for tomorrow’s wardrobe. It’s more than a brand—it’s a movement to preserve craft, empower voices, and weave a brighter future for everyone in our city and beyond.
                    </p>

